<LP>
   NEW YORK -- The average interest rate fell to 8.27% at
Citicorp's $50 million weekly auction of 91-day commercial
paper, or corporate IOUs, from 8.451% at last week's sale.
   Bids totaling $415 million were submitted. All accepted
bids were at 8.27%.
