   NEW YORK -- Marine Midland Banks Inc. said that its
parent, Hongkong &amp; Shanghai Banking Corp. Ltd., invested $200
million in new capital in Marine. The investment is split
evenly between equity and subordinated debt.
   The investment brings Marine's Tier 1 capital (chiefly
