   AMERICAN EXPRESS Co. (New York) -- Patricia Patterson was
named senior vice president of consumer lending for the
American Express Travel Related Services Inc. unit. Ms.
Patterson was assistant general counsel for Travel Related
Services and general counsel for Centurion Bank, another unit
of the travel and financial-services company. In her new
position, she succeeds Craig Hoenshell, who recently was
named president of the Travelers Cheque group.
